---
title: White Cheddar Wonderburgers with Old Bay Roasted Broccoli, Caramelized Onion & Special Sauce
description: What’s the “wonder” in “wonderburger,” you ask? It’s all in the texture! The crispy, craggy edges, achieved when balls of beef are pressed down in a hot pan with a spatula to create super-thin, crispy burgers. Topped with gooey white cheddar, the patties are sandwiched between potato buns with caramelized onion and a homemade special sauce that’s also perfect for pairing with Old Bay fries on the side—and will elicit major “oohs” and “ahhs” from your dining companions.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/635a8d70433b71c1e20cb96a-8040bfea.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/white-cheddar-wonderburgers-635a8d70433b71c1e20cb96a-5280fcbd.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/white-cheddar-wonderburgers-635a8d70433b71c1e20cb96a
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 920 kcal
